---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="App Terms of Service - RoyalPrompts" description="Simple terms of service for RoyalPrompts mobile app - Easy to understand terms for Google Play approval.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">RoyalPrompts App Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        <strong>Last updated:</strong> December 2024
      </p>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 mb-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-green-700">
              <strong>Simple Terms:</strong> These terms are easy to understand. By using RoyalPrompts, you agree to use it responsibly and legally.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. What is RoyalPrompts?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        RoyalPrompts is a mobile app that provides AI-powered writing prompts to help you with creative writing, productivity, and inspiration.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. How to Use the App</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        RoyalPrompts is free to download and use. You can:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Browse and discover AI prompts</li>
        <li>Save your favorite prompts</li>
        <li>Create your own prompts</li>
        <li>Use prompts for your creative projects</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Anonymous Usage</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        You don't need to create an account or provide personal information. The app works with anonymous login:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>No email or password required</li>
        <li>No personal data collection</li>
        <li>Start using immediately after download</li>
        <li>Your data stays on your device</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. What You Can Do</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You may:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Use the app for personal and commercial projects</li>
        <li>Share prompts with others</li>
        <li>Create derivative works using our prompts</li>
        <li>Use the app on multiple devices</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. What You Cannot Do</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You may not:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Use the app for illegal activities</li>
        <li>Try to hack or break the app</li>
        <li>Create harmful or offensive content</li>
        <li>Violate any laws or regulations</li>
        <li>Spam or abuse the app</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Content Ownership</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <strong>Our Content:</strong> The app and its features belong to RoyalPrompts.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <strong>Your Content:</strong> Any prompts you create belong to you. You can use them however you want.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <strong>AI Prompts:</strong> The AI-generated prompts are provided for your use. You can modify and use them in your projects.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. App Availability</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We try to keep the app working 24/7, but sometimes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>The app might be temporarily unavailable for updates</li>
        <li>Your internet connection might affect performance</li>
        <li>We might need to fix bugs or add new features</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We respect your privacy. Please read our <a href="/app-privacy" class="text-royal-600 hover:text-royal-700 underline">Privacy Policy</a> to understand how we handle your data.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Age Requirements</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        RoyalPrompts is safe for all ages. Children under 13 can use the app with parental supervision.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We may update these terms occasionally. We'll notify you through app updates. Continued use means you accept the new terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Questions about these terms? Contact us:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Email:</strong> support@royalprompts.online<br>
          <strong>Response:</strong> Within 48 hours
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">12. Legal Stuff</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> The app is provided "as is." We're not responsible for any issues that might arise from using the app.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <strong>Limitation:</strong> Our liability is limited to the maximum extent permitted by law.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mt-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
              <strong>Simple Summary:</strong> Use RoyalPrompts responsibly and legally. We provide AI prompts to help your creativity. No personal data required. Enjoy creating!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
